title.rendered: Advent Map [0] – Karolier [2K, Java, Bedrock, Download] #Daily Maps

excerpt.rendered:
Karolier is a small island… its 2km by 2km by McMeddon. It’s an Island that is “shaped like a zero”. Completely surrounded by Mountains and oversized beaches to explore. For the first time, rivers thrive through the lands, originating in the snow covered mountains where snow gather between rifts, slowly dripping further down the mountain and finding their way down to the sea as water. Clear shallow cliffs mark the islands edge. Between new mountains, new river systems you find new custom vegetation and stuff to explore.

Make a journey around the island and make your way to new worlds.
The Sea level is at 62 as the default Minecraft generation, which means.. if you take a boat, you will make a near seamless transition between reality and Minecraft.
